      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "This question is specifically about Java though, and <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html#bs\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/&hellip;</a> says &quot;A backslash may be used prior to a non-alphabetic character regardless of whether that character is part of an unescaped construct.&quot;"
    } ],
