    "question_id" : 3674930,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Escape special characters with a backslash. <code>\\.</code>, <code>\\*</code>, <code>\\+</code>, <code>\\\\d</code>, and so on. If you are unsure, you may escape any non-alphabetical character whether it is special or not. See <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html#bs\" rel=\"noreferrer\">the javadoc for java.util.regex.Pattern</a> for further information.</p>\n"
  }, {
