      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Be aware that whether to escape the backslash depends on how you are supplying the regex.  if hardcoded you do need to use: &quot;\\\\.&quot;  , if reading from a raw source (e.g. text file) you use only a single backslash:  \\."
