      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Same, <code>\\\\.</code> didn&#39;t work for me: <code>\\.</code> complained that <code>.</code> doesn&#39;t need to be escaped, <code>\\\\.</code> made it think it was <code>\\.</code> instead of <code>.</code>, <code>\\\\\\.</code> and the builder threw an error, <code>[.]</code> was the only thing that worked."
