    "question_id" : 3674930,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was trying to split using <code>.folder</code>. For this use case, the solution to use <code>\\\\.folder</code> and <code>[.]folder</code> didn't work.</p>\n<p>The following code worked for me</p>\n<pre><code>String[] pathSplited = Pattern.compile(&quot;([.])(folder)&quot;).split(completeFilePath);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 30259952,
      "reputation" : 1,
      "user_id" : 23190186,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/0005574fdf2498234411807c1076eedb?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Zurab",
