    "answer_id" : 78059641,
    "question_id" : 3674930,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use Pattern.quote(&quot;.&quot;).</p>\n<p>In this case, we are treating the &quot;.&quot; as a normal character and not a special regular expression character.</p>\n"
