  "title" : "Java RegEx meta character (.) and ordinary dot?",
  "body" : "<p>In Java RegEx, how to find out the difference between <code>.</code>(dot) the meta character and the normal dot as we using in any sentence. How to handle this kind of situation for other meta characters too like (<code>*</code>,<code>+</code>,<code>\\d</code>,...)</p>\n"
